    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Franck Zibi</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:242px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/franck-zibi-7631b16/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/Franck_Zibi.jpg/240px-Franck_Zibi.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a6/Franck_Zibi.jpg/360px-Franck_Zibi.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a6/Franck_Zibi.jpg/480px-Franck_Zibi.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Franck_Zibi.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Franck Zibi <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Franck Zibi</b>,<br />\na French computer scientist, chess player, and senior developer at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Soci%C3%A9t%C3%A9_G%C3%A9n%C3%A9rale\">Societe Generale</a> Corporate and Investment Banking <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nAs computer chess programmer, he is author of the chess programs <a href=\"/HpChess\" title=\"HpChess\">HpChess</a> for the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HP-48_series\">HP48</a> calculators family written in <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a>, and its successors, the <a href=\"/WinBoard\" title=\"WinBoard\">WinBoard</a> compatible engines <a href=\"/ZChess\" title=\"ZChess\">ZChess</a> and <a href=\"/Pharaon\" title=\"Pharaon\">Pharaon</a>, both written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a>, the latter also <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> conform. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Franck_Zibi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://www.ludochess.com/trn_massy2002/tournoi.php3\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"TigerPharaon2002.jpg\" src=\"/images/a/aa/TigerPharaon2002.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/Massy_2002\" title=\"Massy 2002\">Massy 2002</a>, <a href=\"/Massy_2002#timetrouble\" title=\"Massy 2002\">Round 5</a>, <a href=\"/Chess_Tiger\" title=\"Chess Tiger\">Chess Tiger</a> vs. <a href=\"/Pharaon\" title=\"Pharaon\">Pharaon</a>, Franck Zibi <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ernest_Bonnem&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ernest Bonnem (page does not exist)\">Ernest Bonnem</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Franck_Zibi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=127888\">ANN&#160;: ZChess 2.0 (London) Released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Franck Zibi</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 02, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=186734\">Pharaon 2.50 for WinBoard is available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Franck Zibi</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 01, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=208406\">Pharaon 2.61 is available (with WinBoard and UCI support)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Franck Zibi</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 19, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=403314\">Re: Mail from Franck Zibi</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Franck Zibi</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 30, 2004 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=404644\">Release of Pharaon v3.2</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Franck Zibi</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 08, 2005</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=431772\">Release of Pharaon v3.3 (with Chess 960 support)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Franck Zibi</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 17, 2005</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Franck_Zibi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/franck-zibi-7631b16/\">Franck Zibi | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=650650\">Zibi, Franck FIDE Chess Profile</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/person.php?id=135\">Franck Zibi's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fzibi.com/cchessus.htm\">Franck ZIBI Computer Chess Page</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fzibi.com/cchess/bitboards.htm\">An Introduction to Bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Franck Zibi</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rebel.nl/authors.htm\">Meet the Authors</a> by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fzibi.com/pharaon/exactachess.htm\">“20 Questions” with Franck Zibi (Author of Pharaon)</a>, Questions by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Michael_Diosi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Michael Diosi (page does not exist)\">Michael Diosi</a>, <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christopher_Conkie&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christopher Conkie (page does not exist)\">Christopher Conkie</a>, April 2005</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Franck_Zibi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/franck-zibi-7631b16/\">Franck Zibi | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/franck-zibi-7631b16/\">Franck Zibi | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=232663\">Re: Massy 2002 - Final standings &amp; pictures &amp; pgn at ...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Franck Zibi</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 29, 2002</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=232907\">Massy, from the horse's mouth</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ernest_Bonnem&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ernest Bonnem (page does not exist)\">Ernest Bonnem</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 30, 2002</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228110811\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.019 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 75/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 166/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00